quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  44,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  44,1,Haa Meeem
  44,2,Wal Kitaabil Mubeen
  44,3,Innaaa anzalnaahu fee lailatim mubaarakah; innaa kunnaa munzireen
  44,4,Feehaa yufraqu kullu amrin hakeem
  44,5,Amram min 'indinaaa; innaa kunnaa mursileen
  44,6,Rahmatam mir rabbik; innahoo Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem
  44,7,Rabbis samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa; in kuntum mooqineen
  44,8,Laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa yuhyee� wa yumeetu Rabbukum wa Rabbu aabaaa'ikumul awwaleen
  44,9,Bal hum fee shakkiny yal'aboon
  44,10,Fartaqib Yawma taatis samaaa'u bidukhaanim mubeen
  44,11,Yaghshan naasa haazaa 'azaabun aleem
  44,12,Rabbanak shif 'annal 'azaaba innaa mu'minoon
  44,13,Annaa lahumuz zikraa wa qad jaaa'ahum Rasoolum mubeen
  44,14,Summaa tawallaw 'anhu wa qaaloo mu'allamum majnoon
  44,15,Innaa kaashiful 'azaabi qaleelaa; innakum 'aaa'indoon
  44,16,Yawma nabtishul batsha tal kubraa innaa muntaqimoon
  44,17,Wa laqad fatannaa qablahum qawma Fir'awna wa jaaa'ahum Rasoolun kareem
  44,18,An addooo ilaiya 'ibaadal laahi innee lakum Rasoolun ameen
  44,19,Wa al laa ta'loo 'alal laahi innee aateekum bisultaanim mubeen
  44,20,Wa innee 'uztu bi Rabbee wa rabbikum an tarjumoon
  44,21,Wa il lam tu'minoo lee fa'taziloon
  44,22,Fada'aa rabbahooo anna haaa'ulaaa'i qawmum mujrimoon
  44,23,Fa asri bi'ibaadee lailan innakum muttaba'oon
  44,24,Watrukil bahra rahwan innahum jundum mughraqoon
  44,25,Kam tarakoo min jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
  44,26,Wa zuroo'inw wa maqaa min kareem
  44,27,Wa na'matin kaanoo feehaa faakiheen
  44,28,Kazaalika wa awrasnaahaa qawman aakhareen
  44,29,Famaa bakat 'alaihimus samaaa'u wal ardu wa maa kaanoo munzareen
  44,30,Wa laqad najjainaa Baneee Israaa'eela minal'azaabil muheen
  44,31,Min Fir'awn; innahoo kaana 'aaliyam minal musrifeen
  44,32,Wtarnaahum 'alaa 'ilmin 'alal 'aalameen
  44,33,Wa aatainaahum minal aayaati maa feehi balaaa'um mubeen
  44,34,Inna haaa'ulaaa'i la yaqooloon
  44,35,In hiya illaa mawtatunal oolaa wa maa nahnu bimun shareen
  44,36,Faatoo bi aabaaa'inaaa inkuntum saadiqeen
  44,37,Ahum khayrun am qawmu Tubba'inw wallazeena min qablihim; ahlaknaahum innahum kaanoo mujrimeen
  44,38,Wa maa khalaqnas samaawaati wal arda wa maa baina humaa laa'ibeen
  44,39,Maa khalaqnaahumaaa illaa bilhaqqi wa laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon
  44,40,Inna yawmal fasli meeqaatuhum ajma'een
  44,41,Yawma laa yughnee mawlan 'am mawlan shai'anw wa laa hum yunsaroon
  44,42,Illaa mar rahimal laah' innahoo huwal 'azeezur raheem
  44,43,Inna shajarataz zaqqoom
  44,44,Ta'aamul aseem
  44,45,Kalmuhli yaghlee filbutoon
  44,46,Kaghalyil hameem
  44,47,Khuzoohu fa'tiloohu ilaa sawaaa'il laheem
  44,48,Summa subboo fawqa raasihee min 'azaabil hameem
  44,49,Zuq innaka antal 'azeezul kareem
  44,50,Inna haazaa maa kuntum bihee tamtaroon
  44,51,Innal muttaqeena fee maqaamin ameen
  44,52,Fee jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
  44,53,Yalbasoona min sundusinw wa istbraqim mutaqaabileen
  44,54,Kazaalika wa zawwajnaahum bihoorin 'een
  44,55,Yad'oona feehaa bikulli faakihatin aamineen
  44,56,Laa yazooqoona feehal mawtaa illal mawtatal oolaa wa qaqaahum 'azaabal jaheem
  44,57,Fadlam mir rabbik; zaalika huwal fawzul 'azeem
  44,58,Fa innamaa yassarnaahu bilisaanika la'allahum yatazakkaroon
  44,59,Fartaqib innahum murta qiboon
